<section class="about-section">
    <h2>Company History</h2>
    <p>Founded in 2024, our car rental service has quickly become a trusted name in the automotive rental industry. Our founders, passionate about making transportation accessible and affordable, started with a single vehicle and a dream. Through hard work, dedication, and a commitment to excellent customer service, we have expanded our fleet to over 100 vehicles, ranging from compact cars to luxury SUVs.</p>
    
    <p>We believe in providing our customers with the best possible experience, whether they need a car for a day, a week, or longer. Our user-friendly website and mobile app allow customers to easily browse our fleet, make reservations, and enjoy a seamless rental experience.</p>
    
    <p>At our core, we value reliability, transparency, and customer satisfaction. We strive to maintain the highest standards in service and vehicle quality, ensuring that our customers feel safe and confident on the road.</p>
</section>

